Detects APT29-style low-noise intrusion behavior, including encoded PowerShell, stealth execution chains, and slow periodic communication.

index=endpoint OR index=proxy OR index=sysmon
(
    CommandLine="*EncodedCommand*"
    OR CommandLine="*Invoke-Expression*"
    OR CommandLine="*IEX*"
    OR CommandLine="*http*"
)
| bin _time span=10m
| stats count by src_ip _time host user CommandLine
| eventstats avg(count) as avg stdev(count) as stdev by src_ip
| eval anomaly=if(count > avg + (stdev*2), 1, 0)
| where anomaly=1
| sort - count
